          "ruleIndex": 1,
          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "The GET /api/logs/<user_id> endpoint has no authentication or authorization check. Any caller can supply an arbitrary user_id to retrieve that user's complete audit log history, which contains actions, details (including logged passwords from login events), IP addresses, and timestamps. Implement authentication middleware and verify the caller owns the requested user_id or has admin privileges."
          },
